i want to write a simple library where people can go `import xnumpy as np` instead of `import numpy as np` and have a plug and play replacement thats way faster.

write report

improve readme

outlook:
- lazy expression tracing: instead of executing each operation immediately, record a computation graph (like `Add(Mul(a, x), y)`). materialize the result only when needed (indexing, printing, passing to non-xnumpy code). this is what enables fusion. then we can JIT-compile fused expressions.
